name: FieldPass Tracking
description:
This test suite contains test cases regarding tracking on field pass in an Android device. 
In order to test the tracking, you must have access to wi-fi, an android phone and Charles Proxy or a similar proxying tool. The test cases were built around using Charles, so if you would like to use a different tool, you must be aware of the analogous behavior of the other tool of your choice. It is also important that you have a debug version of the app NOT release version. With release version, you won't be able to track these events.
